{"title":"不朽的碑铭——雨花台烈士雕像颂","authors":["黄东成"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":4,"day":15}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"不朽的碑铭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——雨花台烈士雕像颂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄东成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我倒在血泊里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黎明前的黑暗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吞没血染的姓名。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冥冥中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听动地惊雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔突地火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蹿出三千年板结的土层，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼啸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赤红的世纪风。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我欣慰地倒在雨花台，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接受百花朝觐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有名有姓的默默奉献，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无名无姓的赫赫功勋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不为让历史评说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荆棘丛中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个开拓者的姓名，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但求后人深深领悟血的代价，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"换得这来之不易的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血色黎明。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烈士纪念馆里打开功名录，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长存的浩气扑面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更多的是没有记载的无名氏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共和国的奠基石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旧世界的掘墓人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有姓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有名。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不，生命才是实体。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人的价值，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"属于造福万代的生命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血沃的信念方能使符号植入精神。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命短暂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"精神永恒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别眼热那些自我膨胀的庞然大物，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终被唾沫的浪涛淹没，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为时代不耻；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汩汩血泊中倒下的无私奉献，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却会在亿万人心上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矗立，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"受万代崇敬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赤霞纷飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化作面面旗帜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化作孩子们颈下的红领巾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如茵绿草地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"围成一个鲜红鲜红的巨大花圈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听虔诚的誓辞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举臂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"默对无名无姓的雕像，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼唤一个不朽的姓名，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——共产党人。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":16,"page_end":16}